item.title: Race to the rock
item.description: Race to the rock There are so many ways race to the rock is inspiring and good. For an introduction read about the first 2016 ride. Race to the rock happened again in 2017 and 2018. An active online community emerged quickly that serves up a constant stream of visual inspiration. This post is a little different, but hopefully adds another tasty tidbit to the race-to-the-rock soup.
